s=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„•</span><span class=\"o\">},</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰¤</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">â„•</span><span class=\"bp\">âˆž</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">fun</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">not_lt_bot</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"n\">rfl.le</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
